MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

1. Feedback: all fields mandatory (ratings + text + name); date auto-applied
   at submission (manual date input removed); student name locked to session.
2. Certificate removed from student-facing views (forms portal tabs + student
   hub card); instructors issue certificates.
3. Dedup: Module 4 IO slide (duplicated Module 9's IO landmark) replaced with
   a shock-context IV/IO decision slide deferring technique to Module 9;
   Module 3 BVM card points to Module 9 for OPA/C-E technique.
4. Cohort isolation (UI + rules):
   - hub_instructor: cohort selector scopes roster/stats/CSV to one cohort;
     roster merge now carries examUnlocked/feedback/scores; plain-instructor
     roster load is cohort-scoped.
   - firestore.rules: admins & lead instructors see all cohorts; plain
     instructor limited to own cohort (student cohort resolved via user doc).
     Requires: firebase deploy --only firestore:rules

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01Q1yqa6m3EkyuewpmLQS8PB
